    {
      "category": "Pragmatics",
      "rule": "Introducing yourself in a short profile",
      "description": "A simple self-introduction at A1 level often combines name, age, nationality, city, job or study, and interests.",
      "examples": [
        {
          "it": "Mi chiamo Oscar Bellini, sono argentino e lavoro in un'agenzia immobiliare.",
